Package: ClinicalUtils
Title: Clinical Data Processing Utilities for Clinical Trials
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Justin", "Zhang", 
           email = "justin@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for clinical trial data processing,
    analysis, and reporting. This package provides utilities for CDISC SDTM/ADaM
    data manipulation, pharmacometric analysis, regulatory submission preparation,
    and clinical trial workflow automation. Designed for pharmaceutical and
    clinical research environments with focus on reproducibility, validation,
    and compliance with regulatory standards.
